---
source: crates/shipper-cargo-failure/src/lib.rs
expression: "format!(\"retryable: {}\\npermanent: {}\\nambiguous: {}\", retryable.message, permanent.message, ambiguous.message)"
---
retryable: transient failure (retryable)
permanent: permanent failure (fix required)
ambiguous: publish outcome ambiguous; registry did not show version
